    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fixed-rate low-interest government backed loan up to \u00a320,000 for every UK adult",
        "additional_details": "Following years of austerity, the destabilising effect of Brexit and the current Covid-19 crisis affecting us all the economy is deteriorating from its previous already stagnant status. The people are suffering, across all backgrounds.\r\n\r\nIn these unprecedented times an economic reset is required and therefore I put forward this suggestion to ensure our economy can quickly recover and grow after the current crisis abates.",
        "background": "A simple and widespread solution to the economic crisis caused by Covid-19\r\n\r\nThis would be not dependant on credit score, housing situation or employment status \u2013 as long as the applicant can satisfy that they have an income to repay the debt.",
